37 SECTION 2.11.(a) The cost-of-living adjustments authorized by this act:
38 (1) For the 2025-2026 fiscal year, shall be paid effective on July 1, 2025, and do
39 not apply to persons separated from service due to resignation, dismissal,
40 reduction in force, death, or retirement or whose last workday is prior to June
