48 forty thousand dollars ($408,040,000) in recurring funds for the 2025-2026
49 fiscal year.
50 (2) Effective July 1, 2025, there is appropriated from the General Fund to the
51 Reserve for Compensation Increases the sum of five hundred forty-three
